highlights.text: “Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 124 weeks straight.
“EARFQUAKE” by Tyler, The Creator is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #6.
“Hold Me While You Wait” by Lewis Capaldi is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 68 spots at #125.
Billie Eilish has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “bad guy” is the highest at #2.
